text: is a railway station on the Gotōji Line in Tagawa, Fukuoka, Japan, operated by Kyushu Railway Company (JR Kyushu). ==Lines== Funao Station is served by the Gotōji Line. ==Adjacent stations== ==See also== * List of railway stations in Japan ==References== ==External links== * Category:Railway stations in Fukuoka Prefecture Category:Railway stations in Japan opened in 1922
